    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Empty lots. Blackened buildings. Dimly lit hallways.<br>They all live and breathe just as we do.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/88ea0915cd72bc0c60691e7d83779326.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br>Welcome to <strong>Interior Worlds</strong>; an ambient first person exploration game where you'll dive into strange, yet familiar spaces. Temporary gaps and portals we cross at some point or another - now yearning for a closer look. A look that can only be seen properly through the lens of an SLR camera.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/09d0af7316f7c116c51c7d11c0468863.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/2c936ca8e0f14ee93c17a851cd8f81c5.poster.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/2c936ca8e0f14ee93c17a851cd8f81c5.webm?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/2c936ca8e0f14ee93c17a851cd8f81c5.mp4?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your vintage and mysterious analog camera to capture stunning photographs of environmental anomalies throughout each space. Keep a sharp eye out while traversing the more... unsettling locations.<br></li><li>Track and share your own in-game catalog of photos, pre-filtered with subtle layers of peak liminal crust.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/0db98d2a368c12169bb7007543c6d37d.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/a4a881fc14e8b3ace3299dbd690e3543.poster.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/a4a881fc14e8b3ace3299dbd690e3543.webm?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/a4a881fc14e8b3ace3299dbd690e3543.mp4?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>Ten unique thresholds to traverse</i></strong>. A roadside hotel, empty movie theater, dying mall, and many more. Every environment is hand-crafted in a loving throwback to late 90's and early 00's graphics.<br></li><li><strong><i>Unparalleled interactivity</i></strong>. Activate vending machines, phones, sinks, televisions, or simply turn the lights on or off for a different photo-moment vibe.<br></li><li><strong><i>Immersive and unsettling soundscape</i></strong>. Melt into an eerie mix of low, rumbling drones and soft, stretched pads during the journey.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/399a8307d8e6549596bc4f0fc860d1fc.poster.avif?t=1748113634\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/399a8307d8e6549596bc4f0fc860d1fc.webm?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296800/extras/399a8307d8e6549596bc4f0fc860d1fc.mp4?t=1748113634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
